ants.\n\nNo Italian regions are in the white zone yet. As of the latest order signed by Health Minister Roberto Speranza, most of Italy is now a yellow zone, while five regions are orange. (Xinhua/RSS)","title":"Italy extends state of emergency as COVID-19 deaths exceed 80,000 - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/14/156230/","video":[]}
